', w, v₁, v₂, u₁, u₂}</a> <span class=\"fn\">G</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Limits/Preserves/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Limits.ReflectsLimitsOfSize\">ReflectsLimitsOfSize.{w', w, v₁, v₂, u₁, u₂}</a> <span class=\"fn\">G</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"If `C` has limits and `G` preserves limits, then if `G` reflects isomorphisms then it reflects\nlimits.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Limits/Preserves/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Limits.reflectsLimits_of_reflectsIsomorphisms","kind":"theorem","line":593,"name":"CategoryTheory.Limits.reflectsLimits_of_reflectsIsomorphisms","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Limits/Preserves/Basic.lean#L593-L599"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Limits/Preserves/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Limits.reflectsLimitsOfShape_of_reflectsIsomorphisms\"><span class=\"name\">CategoryTheory</span>.<span class=\"name\">Limits</span>.<span class=\"name\">reflectsLimitsOfShape_of_reflectsIsomorphisms</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">C</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u₁}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Category\">Category.{v₁, u₁}</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">D</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u₂}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class